name: TRIBE NFT CHARACTERS : Common 001
description: TRIBE NFT CHARACTERS is the first collection of NFT artworks created by the Dutch collective, SMACK. Comprised of 500 individuals, the series derives from their digital piece, TRIBE TRIPTYCH, a super information landscape which explores identity and mass behaviour. //  500 collectible characters based on their rarity level Five rarity levels expressed through background colour  COMMON = GREY. // RARE = GREEN. // EPIC = BLUE. // LEGENDARY = RED. // MYTHICAL = ORANGE. //   The rarity level determines the number of characters and the available editions of each.  COMMON = 250 characters / Edition of 20 / Medium: PNG, 3840x3840 pixels.
